title: NFL ATL: OTA whispers
itunes:title: NFL ATL: OTA whispers
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- breaks down all the reviews, reactions and rumors from this week’s batch of organized team activities.  Elsewhere, as always, the gang picks apart all the biggest headlines from around the league.
